The Grecian influence on footwear never goes out of style; it belongs in the aisle of classic
column17: go-to-footwear whether you are a hot shot corporate woman or a laid-back traveller. These Catwalk Flats are designed with a dust and yellow body that complements the Indian skin tone with much ease and adds exuberance. The elastic strap at the middle of these flats gives you great grip even while walking long distance. These Catwalk Flats allow you versatile styling options
column18:
go all out with cute chinos and a sheer blouse or shorts and a tee.

Footwear from Catwalk are characterised by swanky designs and comfort that add a classy zing to your overall attire.
